{"tid":472114,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得自己好廢好冇毅力","createTime":"2017-11-18T02:01:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-24T16:41:22.000Z","uid":65439,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e9594f79e703650664deff19c93ffc3cee7b5024","tid":472114,"uid":65439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T02:01:35.000Z","msg":"我發覺自己真係好廢又懶<br />\n有時遇到d事比較難同埋繁複就會逃避<br />\n成日都捱唔住 好冇毅力<br />\n例如 試過返過幾份工<br />\n次次初頭學野個陣<br />\n已經因為好煩好多野記就想quit<br />\n每次返工都會好壓抑 好悲傷咁 會想喊<br />\n尤其是坐緊車 見住成班冇靈魂既人一齊去返工<br />\n真係好恐怖<br />\n<br />\n所以有時好憎自己咁易放棄 又唔捱得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個心係好似純粹唔想做野咁 我知人係要做野<br />\n但我控制唔到自己既情緒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <span style=\"color: pink;\">有輕微抑鬱</span><br />\n完全唔知自己想點 好憎自己"},{"pid":"941b7f7285f1d7058e20888fafad9b4f51fc3260","tid":472114,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T02:05:12.000Z","msg":"習慣就好，你要明白自己就係一條廢柴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59914dd40e45b701ff4c901a5f4c9eccfbe844c8","tid":472114,"uid":65439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T02:18:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>習慣就好，你要明白自己就係一條廢柴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實我都知自己廢<br />\n但估唔到原來廢成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人人都捱到 甚至覺得輕鬆<br />\n得我呢個廢柴捱唔到要quit咁制<br />\n好憎自己"},{"pid":"03f9a3a20516b8e8d6781ced7cb47037df6997c0","tid":472114,"uid":53421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T02:19:45.000Z","msg":"你"},{"pid":"486c8ec411f54b6e2d47cf84d44e6fa3b56449a0","tid":472114,"uid":139272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T02:29:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我發覺自己真係好廢又懶<br />\n有時遇到d事比較難